resources.description: AirBase data products on EEA Data Service

name: data_airbase-the-european-air-quality-database-1
description: AirBase is the air quality information system maintained by the EEA through the European topic centre on Air and Climate Change. It contains air quality data delivered annually under 97/101/EC Council Decision establishing a reciprocal exchange of information and data from networks and individual stations measuring ambient air pollution within the Member States (EoI Decision).
title: AirBase - The European air quality database
